node.text:
Hangin’ in hammocks relaxin’ all cool 😎

We are spending A LOT of time outdoors and in our backyard this summer. Thanks to @SerestoUS, for helping protect Harlow and the gang from fleas and ticks! 

We like Seresto® flea and tick collars because they are easy to use and comfortable for both our dogs and our cats to wear. They are also veterinarian recommended, which gives us so much peace of mind. 

Talk to your veterinarian about Seresto® if you have any questions—they are the best source for learning more about flea and tick prevention for both dogs and cats. 🐶🐱#AD

node.text:
#ad Harlow could not contain her excitement when the messenger owl delivered a package with her name on it! Inside?! Her very own Google Nest Cam!

As crazy pet parents, we don't like being away from our animals much. The Nest Cam allows us to be close to them, even when we aren't at home! Not only are we able to live stream video 24/7 over Wi-Fi on our mobile devices, we can talk AND listen to what Harlow and siblings have to say, er, woof with the Nest’s 2-way audio feature.

The Nest Cam comes with intelligent alerts which notify us about what truly matters in our house-when our pets are being adorable and when they are taking selfies! 
Share your own #NestPets video with #CaughtOnNestCam for a chance to be featured on @madebygoogle
